## Tailwind CSS Patterns

### Color Scheme
- **Primary**: `blue-600`, `blue-700` (buttons, links)
- **Success**: `green-600`, `green-50` (success messages)
- **Error**: `red-600`, `red-50` (error messages)
- **Neutral**: `gray-600`, `gray-900` (text)
- **Background**: `gray-50`, `white` (backgrounds)

### Button Patterns
```typescript
// Primary button
className="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"

// Secondary button
className="bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-blue-600 font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-blue-600 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"

// Disabled button
className="bg-gray-400 cursor-not-allowed opacity-50"
```

### Form Patterns
```typescript
// Input field
className="appearance-none block w-full px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm"

// Label
className="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700"

// Error message container
className="rounded-md bg-red-50 p-4"
```

### Layout Patterns
```typescript
// Page container
className="min-h-screen bg-gray-50"

// Content container
className="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"

// Card container
className="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6"

// Centered content
className="flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
```

### Responsive Design
- Use mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`
- Common patterns: `sm:flex-row`, `md:grid-cols-3`, `lg:px-8`

### Accessibility
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Include proper ARIA labels
- Ensure keyboard navigation
- Use proper focus states
- Maintain color contrast ratios

